::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica frowns. He didn't know the geography of the area too well, but he 
knew enough to get around.

"Uh, I think the Pred ship might be closer," he replies to Phobia's question, 
"But it was taken over by Rampage, and even it it wasn't, your escort left," 
he says, meaning Tarantulus.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Bloodystrike turns his head to look at Stranato, Inzola, and Burning Hammer.

"Me and Rep are trying to help these Preds out, on Zardus' orders. I thought 
you three returned to base."
